author: The Critical Drinker
description: He was once a wrestling superstar and the king of the box office, pulling in hundreds of millions of dollars per year, endorsed by everyone and so popular he actually considered running for President. So what happened to The Rock? How did he go from one of the most beloved stars of all time, to an ageing lolcow? Let's find out.
title: Crash And Burn - Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson
